title: Leading Youtubers from the Netherlands based on subscribers 2018
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Number of subscribers in thousands for 10 number of Months.
Month Trap City has the highest Number of subscribers in thousands and Tiësto has the lowest Number of subscribers in thousands.
The maximum Month Trap City has got 3.75 times higher Number of subscribers in thousands than the minimum Month Tiësto.
